{"type": "article", "id": 42692, "title": "阿迪发布曼联队服，以及，Chanel 秋冬高定系列发布 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-05T02:33:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 429, "name": "蜘蛛侠"}, {"id": 991, "name": "New Balance"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 16038, "name": "BAPE"}, {"id": 35126, "name": "Ultraboost"}, {"id": 42065, "name": "日本零售"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 14652, "name": "赫斯特"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170705095645QUKiPeBFalnMH1r0.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/japan-retailers-increased-sales-june-10937970/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>日本零售商六月业绩普遍上涨</strong></a> | 在海外游客不断增加和夏季促销的刺激下，日本的化妆品、珠宝、服饰甚至百货业 6 月份的销售额都有所增长。优衣库的母公司迅销集团周二发布 6 月数据表示，销售额上涨了 4.1%，消费者数量增长了 8.2%。日本百货公司三越伊势丹 6 月份的销售额增长了 1.1%，高岛屋则实现了 4.6% 的增长。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/arnault-family-ups-christian-dior-stake-94-22-percent-10938446/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LVMH 的老板 Arnault 家族对 Dior 的收购基本完成，持股份额增至 94.2%</strong></a> | 早在今年四月，LVMH 的董事长兼首席执行官 Bernard Arnault 的家族就宣布以 121 亿欧元的价格收购 Dior 集团剩余的 26% 股权，简化 LVMH 的所有权结构。据法国金融市场管理局 AMF 所称，Bernard Arnault 家族已收购 Dior 集团剩余的 3640 万股股份，持股份额已从此前的 74.3% 提升至 94.2%，并拥有 96.5% 的投票权。 </p><p><a href=\"http://m.ftchinese.com/story/001073171\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>赫斯特传媒集团试水中国投资市场，关注新技术</strong></a> | 旗下拥有《ELLE》，《嘉人》，《睿士》等杂志的传媒集团已经进入中国资本市场。据赫斯特资本中国区总经理胡盈青称，目前赫斯特在中国投的两个项目，一个是酷家乐，一个是英语流利说。未来，赫斯特还将继续关注新技术发展，例如 AR、智能出行，电商和数字媒体等业务也会考虑。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/manchester-united-2017-18-home-kit\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 正式发布曼联 2017-18 赛季主场队服</a>。新球衣采用了极简设计风格，并融入了 climacool 透气技术。adidas 经典的三条纹出现在肩膀位置，袖口的红、白、黑条纹设计，代表「红魔」血统，也象征了比赛日 Old Trafford 飘扬的主队旗帜。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100038OKDwloFNujCvd79a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100038DdSRmHF1nJrN39WA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100039HUmruKOPRJcVh1DI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100039gHVd6Z471BmaNMLT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100039emPx6BRiMV0SKj2c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100105f1xDZmRJsUoMc3Kh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/bape-2017-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">BAPE 2017 秋冬系列 lookbook 将于 7 月 8 日正式上架</a>。除了经典的迷彩、猿人头和鲨鱼图案之外，还融入了丹宁、条纹、豹纹及复古运动风等丰富元素，来看看： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100008W8jkt7bye0uoOHha.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100008Ml15ATh2CIKBk6xz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100008DMu5heOpfdGo8Qn4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100008QqEYZuVAFaK0jU9o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100008o7TgWsLl3Id41KB5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100008O7JiQHCZxTVshc1e.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100009Rm7kUN5CAV4qfHwd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100009GKxEFI9wAd0lmPgk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100009sKon5A2EhMJQ89DO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100009drlBpOof70SeI3GJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100010O4i1yWVhGnEgNptL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100010DriSnfZoYwkTl1IH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100010MNcuOhVtf4ompTgD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100010q0d8eOtl7MFEDsvY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100010FhKfDH2azTILxpcB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100010zopjrUi7Qxk1BEMt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100011J1uvEjfHDboeyqsY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707051000115DUQidoGp1nBbcqN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/marvel-new-balance-530-spider-man\" rel=\"nofollow\">《蜘蛛侠：英雄归来》上映之际，漫威与 New Balance 展开合作，推出了蜘蛛侠配色的 530 跑鞋</a>。该鞋款目前已在 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.baitme.com/new-balance-x-marvel-men-spider-man-smu-mrl530sm-burgundy-nbmrl530sm-80\" rel=\"nofollow\">BAIT</a> 独家限量发售，鞋面是蜘蛛网纹路，在鞋带扣和鞋垫上可以看到漫威的标志点缀，定价为 125 美元。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095941NTjPszyMbZ07E3C4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095941TcC0ikp96EhBlFVx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707050959415zrwDRYIv4O2nxtf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095945OXBvSzCDUay7PGTA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>昨日，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-couture-2017/paris/chanel/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel 在巴黎大皇宫的 2017 秋冬高级定制秀场</a>上，老佛爷为它搬来了一座“埃菲尔铁塔”。模特们戴着帽子，搭配短靴或长靴，演绎了一如既往优雅的 Chanel 高定系列。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095855sAmkL21nz3TYxuvQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095855DoMt2mXVg1BI3rpO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095855weoHSh394maCIOs1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095855fBKyJQC3mvESnHFh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707050958550kX7V3ero8blJ4vK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.525622\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017070509585637NlWMEzef01dtbj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095857PcI5MH2aRjf73gVm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095857Q4HIUtZRGS8uzM2C.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095858rdAIXqNp1F75VkS2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095858R14ic96TGQjLnDPp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095859tQYyi7c34LezdxWM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095900My3JTcsfd42Ov5Aa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095900z5jhZRawmWBdUXbl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095901tXPbUQrNRhCAgF8H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.551977\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095900QB1RqrK6Zag4jAob.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.551515\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095901YFb3TX4riPcEZD76.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095902cn7MsFDiKr81lGkP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095903tv0eFaMiCgqGk6Tf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095904yzho6TLk9FEn0GXA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707050959040hkm7vdFWzXtaO6l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.546120\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095905RVs7ierIU9gZ3TdN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095906imqdZpSBAKbYJRQN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095907eAu4V5DNGqfk8oEL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095907wMiRGqx6ADUSBtne.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502568\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095907npINJDFdTq2EPgem.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502568\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/adidas-ultraboost-uncaged-coral\" rel=\"nofollow\">aididas UltraBOOST Uncaged 出了几款全新配色</a>。包括女生专属的珊瑚色 Coral，以及清爽的 Energy Aqua。与后跟同色调透明支架成为新款配色的一大特点，它也许会是 UltraBOOST 家族接下来的新元素。 </p><p>新配色版本将于 7 月 8 日起正式发售，定价为 180 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100818aqmLib5hIfWlEgn8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100819hU2L0fPajT1WJH4N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707051008216yhG10AXtnMCxzlq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100818nZP1g8ozCjlS5FRi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100819dv6DpOQg0sjU5lyz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707051008186sDAlnFpXaJ5e7Mq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705100819S3cA71LZKTiEGmNY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/louis-vuitton-supreme-pop-up-locations-dates\" rel=\"nofollow\">LV x Supreme 发布多个快闪店的全新地址</a>，当中包括纽约、温哥华、夏威夷等地，而美国地区的快闪店将于 7 月 14 日限定开放一天，而其他旧有的地区将依旧至 7 月 13 日完结。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170705095809B0Cpdg3Ol2TMKeXH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/fall-couture-2017/paris/chanel/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}